        <div facs="#eSc_textblock_9478645f">
            <lb />
            <seg type="topic" resp="#np" ana="#distinction_from_mechanical">
                <hi rendition="#in">U</hi>ntil the Welte-Mignon
                <lb />made its appearance all the
                <lb />piano-playing <sic>'</sic>instruments
                <lb />aimed at making the interpretation
                <lb />of a piece of music mechanically
                <lb />correct;
            </seg>
            the Welte-Mignon<lb />caught the great masters in the act of<lb />playing,
            and <seg ana="#immortality" resp="#np" type="topic">fixed their style for ever</seg>. 
        </div>
